data.description: Motivated Seller! Don't miss the opportunity to own a beautiful 2 story home located in the Fox Moor Subdivision. This home features a spacious kitchen with gorgeous upgraded cabinets and granite countertops. All appliances are included, and the kitchen island features a built-in microwave. On the main floor a cozy fireplace awaits. The beautiful staircase which leads to the upper level, features 4 spacious bedroom rooms. Finished two car garage. An unfinished basement waits for you to add your special touch. This home is located in a great community, just off US-30, with short drives to shopping, restaurants, and much more.
